  ('dietitian-moex-11080', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '周小姐，年三十五，身高 162公分，體重54 公斤，活動量屬中度，根據我國每日營養素建議攝取量，周小姐一天所 需熱能約為多少大卡？ 2300  2100  1900  1700', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11081', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '設計養老院之菜單時，應注意老人飲食特性。在口味上設計宜選用： 較淡的菜  較重口味的菜  西式的菜  較酸的菜', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11082', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '李小姐19歲，身高163公分，是大學一年級學生。下課後每天在速食店打工3小時。請參考附表，計算出她維持理 想體重每日需要攝取的能量為多少大卡？ 附表、不同工作量每日每公斤體重所需的熱量 每日所需能量 工作量  舉例 （kcal/kg IBW/day） 輕度  30  工作時間大都坐著很少站立走動，如：辦事員。 中度  35  工作有時需站立走動，如：學生、老師。 重度  40  工作時間大都站著、走動，如：護士、課後打工需站立的學生屬之。 2336  2044  1752  1460', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11083', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那種食物熱量最高？ 全脂牛奶1杯（240cc）    素炒青江菜（青江菜100公克，油1小匙） 蜜汁蕃薯（蕃薯120公克，糖1大匙）  白蘿蔔湯（白蘿蔔100公克，水100公克）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
